application

Class Company

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.Company

  • public class Company
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is an array-based container class that implements the employee database. The array stores a list of employees (full-time, part-time, management) and grows by 4 if it is full. Methods used in this class are grow(), find(), add(), remove(), setHours(), processPayments(), print(), sortByDept() printByDepartment(), sortByDate(), printByDate(), exportDatabase(), and getNumEmployee().
    Author:
    Jasmin Kaur, Jonathan Delin
